						<div class="postbody">To solve that problem, I think it would be worthwhile to develop an emulator whose mappers are just simple script files. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /> That way, anyone could make whatever custom mapper they wanted, and you could add more mappers to the emulator without it requiring a complete rebuild. As an added bonus, make it cross-platform. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" /></div>

					
